FANNTool is a GUI to the FANN library which allows its easy usage without the need o programming. 

FANNTool distrubuted with executable form for windows But FANNTool is a Cross-Platform.
So you can compile it for your Operating System.

to Compile it

Requirements

FLTK 1.3 : http://www.fltk.org/software.php?VERSION=1.3.0
FANN 2.2 : http://leenissen.dk/fann/wp/download/

if compiling is difficult for you 
install Wine ( http://www.winehq.org/download )
and Run windows version with Wine